level=info json=false\r\n    [INFO] [07-13|07:50:38.148] Build info                               git_branch=heads/v2.48.0 git_tag=v2.48.0-dirty git_commit=084acc1af2e853ee4a57dbdd6920b6a1e58ef85c\r\n    [INFO] [07-13|07:50:38.148] Starting Erigon on Bor Mainnet... \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nCould one of the following erigon parameters help with this? I got them by `erigon --help | grep mem`\r\n>\r\n    --clique.snapshots value                                 number of recent vote snapshots to keep in memory (default: 1024)\r\n    --clique.signatures value                                number of recent block signatures to keep in memory (default: 16384)",
